snippet: Sixteen players were separated by only three shots at the Tampa Bay Championship, with Justin Leonard, Kevin Streelman and George Coetzee leading.
abstract: Justin Leonard, Kevin Streelman and George Coetzee share third-round lead at Tampa Bay Championship in Palm Harbor, Fla; other golf news noted.
